556
00:28:54,650 --> 00:28:57,610
- 家族通病  - 我沒有指責你的意思
- It's a family trait. - Oh, I wasn't being critical.

557
00:28:57,620 --> 00:28:58,890
如果您繼續這樣  先生
If you continue like this, sir,

