I expected to see you a few days ago about the Manor House case.

575
00:29:40,450 --> 00:29:42,540
我覺得那案子你會有點力不從心
I thought you might be a little out of your depth there.

576
00:29:42,540 --> 00:29:44,020
沒有  我解決了
No. I solved it.

577
00:29:44,020 --> 00:29:46,620
