578
00:29:46,630 --> 00:29:48,180
嫉妒殺人
Murderous jealousy.

579
00:29:48,180 --> 00:29:50,760
他給皇家天文學會寫了一篇
He'd written a paper for the Royal Astronomical Society

580
00:29:50,760 --> 00:29:53,020
關於黃赤交角的論文
on the obliquity of the ecliptic,

581
00:29:53,020 --> 00:29:54,170
然後又讀到另一篇
and then read another

582
00:29:54,170 --> 00:29:55,840
比他寫的好的
that seemed to surpass it.

583
00:29:55,840 --> 00:29:56,840
我知道  我讀了
I know, I read it.

584
00:29:56,840 --> 00:29:58,170
你看明白了嗎
Did you understand it?

585
00:29:58,220 --> 00:30:00,640
當然  很淺顯易懂
Yes, of course I understood it, it was perfectly simple.

586
00:30:00,640 --> 00:30:03,140
不是  你明白嫉妒殺人嗎
No, did you understand the murderous jealousy?

587
00:30:03,280 --> 00:30:04,490
一個偉大的頭腦
It is no easy thing

588
00:30:04,500 --> 00:30:07,840
去思忖一個更偉大的頭腦可不容易
for a great mind to contemplate a still greater one.

589
00:30:09,450 --> 00:30:11,880
你召我來就是為了羞辱我嗎
Did you summon me here just to humiliate me?

590
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:13,050
是的
Yes.

591
00:30:13,250 --> 00:30:15,760
當然不是  但這是最大的樂趣
Of course not, but it is by far the greater pleasure.

592
00:30:15,760 --> 00:30:17,410
那你能不能解釋下為什麼要召...
Then would you mind explaining exactly why you did summon...?

593
00:30:17,410 --> 00:30:20,720
我們的生活方式被一個無形敵人所威脅
Our way of life is under threat from an invisible enemy.

594
00:30:21,040 --> 00:30:23,960
他們每天都常伴我們身邊
One that hovers at our elbow on a daily basis.

595
00:30:24,260 --> 00:30:26,010
這些敵人無處不在
These enemies are everywhere...

596
00:30:26,740 --> 00:30:28,000
無人發現
undetected...

597
00:30:28,990 --> 00:30:30,730
無法阻止
and unstoppable.

598
00:30:30,910 --> 00:30:32,150
社會主義者嗎
Socialists?

599
00:30:32,530 --> 00:30:34,780
不是社會主義者  醫生  不是
Not socialists, Doctor, no.

600
00:30:34,780 --> 00:30:36,110
- 無政府主義者  - 不是
- Anarchists? - No.

601
00:30:36,110 --> 00:30:38,570
法國人  婦女參政權論者
The French? The suffragists?

602
00:30:38,890 --> 00:30:41,490
有哪個大規模團體不讓你擔心嗎
Is there any large body of people you're not concerned about?

603
00:30:41,490 --> 00:30:44,570
華生醫生永遠心懷警惕  詳說
Dr Watson is endlessly vigilant. Elaborate...

604
00:30:44,570 --> 00:30:45,970
不  去調查
No. Investigate.

605
00:30:45,970 --> 00:30:48,720
這是我的推測  我需要你去證實
This is a conjecture of mine, I need you to confirm it.

606
00:30:48,720 --> 00:30:50,370
我要給你個案子
I'm sending you a case.

607
00:30:50,380 --> 00:30:52,460
- 蘇格蘭人  - 蘇格蘭人
- The Scots? - The Scots?!

608
00:30:52,730 --> 00:30:54,560
你是否瞭解最近
Are you aware of recent theories concerning

609
00:30:54,570 --> 00:30:56,050
關於妄想症的理論
what is known as paranoia?

610
00:30:56,050 --> 00:30:57,740
聽著像是塞爾維亞人
Oh, sounds Serbian.

611
00:30:58,040 --> 00:31:00,780
會有位女士去找你  卡邁克夫人
A woman will call on you. Lady Carmichael.

612
00:31:00,780 --> 00:31:02,210
