615
00:31:05,740 --> 00:31:07,540
我們不會打敗他們
We don't defeat them.

616
00:31:07,540 --> 00:31:09,700
我們絕對要輸給他們
We most certainly lose to them.

617
00:31:10,220 --> 00:31:11,240
為什麼
Why?

618
00:31:13,450 --> 00:31:16,950
因為他們是正確的  我們是錯的
Because they are right. And we are wrong.

619
00:31:18,120 --> 00:31:20,110
卡邁克夫人的案子  是什麼
Lady Carmichael's case, what is it?

620
00:31:20,110 --> 00:31:22,740
放心  會有值得你注意的地方
Rest assured, it has features of interest.

621
00:31:22,740 --> 00:31:25,090
