On one condition. Have another plum pudding.

629
00:31:41,600 --> 00:31:42,930
本來就準備吃了
There's one on the way.

630
00:31:42,930 --> 00:31:44,620
兩年十一個月四天
Two years, 11 months and four days.

631
00:31:44,620 --> 00:31:49,260
開始好玩嘍  滴答  滴答  滴答
Ha, it's getting exciting now! Ticktock, ticktock, ticktock.

632
00:31:52,940 --> 00:31:55,000
謝謝  懷爾德
Thank you, Wilder.

633
00:31:55,000 --> 00:31:58,100
有一位梅勒斯先生要見您  福爾摩斯先生
Also, a Mr Melas to see you, Mr Holmes.

634
00:31:58,790 --> 00:32:01,440
等我五分鐘  我還有一場賭局要贏呢
Give me five minutes, I have a wager to win.

635
00:32:04,210 --> 00:32:07,040
還是十五分鐘吧
Better make that 15.

636
00:32:08,440 --> 00:32:09,910
滴答
Ticktock.

637
00:32:13,720 --> 00:32:16,310
福爾摩斯先生  我是來請您出主意的
Mr Holmes, I have come here for advice.

638
00:32:16,430 --> 00:32:18,660
