Death.

665
00:33:56,920 --> 00:33:57,810
什麼
What?

666
00:33:58,230 --> 00:33:59,990
這意味著死亡
It means death.

667
00:34:03,980 --> 00:34:07,660
沒什麼  沒什麼
Er, nothing, it's, it's nothing.

668
