It's nothing!

671
00:34:17,960 --> 00:34:18,700
尤斯塔斯
Eustace...

672
00:34:18,700 --> 00:34:20,180
信封您還留著嗎
Did you keep the envelope?

673
00:34:20,530 --> 00:34:23,370
被我丈夫毀了  但上面什麼也沒有
My husband destroyed it, but it was blank.

674
00:34:23,370 --> 00:34:25,100
沒有姓名  位址  任何資訊
No name or address of any kind.

675
00:34:25,550 --> 00:34:28,260
尤斯塔斯爵士在美國待過嗎
Tell me, has Sir Eustace spent time in America?

676
00:34:29,100 --> 00:34:31,590
