- No. - Not even before your marriage?

677
00:34:31,590 --> 00:34:33,140
據我所知沒有
Well, not to my knowledge.

678
00:34:34,900 --> 00:34:37,850
請您繼續往下說吧
Pray, continue with your fascinating narrative.

679
00:34:39,620 --> 00:34:42,710
這是上週一早上的事
Well, that incident took place last Monday morning.

680
00:34:43,050 --> 00:34:44,900
兩天后的週三
It was two days later on the Wednesday

681
00:34:44,900 --> 00:34:46,740
我丈夫第一次看見了她
that my husband first saw her.

682
00:34:47,810 --> 00:34:48,690
誰
Who?

683
00:34:53,620 --> 00:34:54,740
尤斯塔斯
Eustace?

684
00:35:00,640 --> 00:35:02,800
她來找我了  路易莎
She's come for me, Louisa!

685
00:35:03,510 --> 00:35:06,310
天啊  幫幫我  我的罪孽找上門了
Oh, God, help me, my sins have found me out!

686
00:35:06,310 --> 00:35:10,260
誰來找你了  尤斯塔斯  你嚇到我了
Who's come for you? Eustace, you're frightening me.

687
00:35:10,430 --> 00:35:12,480
看啊  看啊
Well, look, look!

688
00:35:16,350 --> 00:35:17,870
你沒看見嗎
Don't you see her?

689
00:35:18,650 --> 00:35:20,370
我誰也沒看見
No, I see no-one.

690
00:35:26,090 --> 00:35:27,130
不見了
Gone.

691
00:35:31,310 --> 00:35:34,550
