693
00:35:37,650 --> 00:35:38,990
是她
It was her!

694
00:35:41,140 --> 00:35:43,980
是鬼新娘
It was the Bride!

695
00:35:45,710 --> 00:35:47,150
而您什麼也沒看見
And you saw nothing?

696
00:35:47,360 --> 00:35:48,250
是的
Nothing.

