1198
01:05:21,430 --> 01:05:23,310
艾米麗婭·瑞克萊蒂  我在搜她
Emelia Ricoletti, I'm looking her up.

1199
01:05:24,010 --> 01:05:25,520
好吧  也許是該看看
Oh, I suppose we should.

1200
01:05:25,730 --> 01:05:28,660
我有許可權查詢軍情五處的絕密資料庫
I have access to the top level of the MI5 archive.

1201
01:05:28,660 --> 01:05:30,290
對  我正在那兒搜索
Yep, that's where I'm looking.

1202
01:05:31,820 --> 01:05:34,400
你認為軍情五處的防火牆怎麼樣
What do you think of MI5 security?

1203
01:05:35,240 --> 01:05:37,520
弄一個也挺好的
I think it would be a good idea.

1204
01:05:38,560 --> 01:05:40,710
艾米麗婭·瑞克萊蒂  "懸案"
Emelia Ricoletti, "Unsolved",

1205
01:05:41,130 --> 01:05:41,980
跟他說的一樣
like he says.

1206
01:05:41,980 --> 01:05:43,710
你們能不能閉嘴五分鐘
Could you all just shut up for five minutes!

1207
01:05:43,710 --> 01:05:44,950
我必須回去
I have to go back.

1208
01:05:45,140 --> 01:05:45,900
我就快破案了
I was nearly there before

1209
01:05:45,900 --> 01:05:47,810
結果讓你們跑進來吵沒了
you stepped on and started yapping away!

1210
01:05:47,810 --> 01:05:50,400
吵  抱歉  我們是打擾你治療了嗎
"Yapping?" Sorry, did we interrupt your session?

1211
01:05:50,630 --> 01:05:51,820
夏洛克  聽我說
Sherlock, listen to me.

1212
01:05:51,820 --> 01:05:53,300
不想聽  你越說越來勁
No, it only encourages you.

1213
01:05:53,300 --> 01:05:55,430
- 我沒生你的氣  - 我真松了口氣啊
- I'm not angry with you. - Oh, that's a relief!

1214
01:05:55,430 --> 01:05:57,950
我本來還挺擔心呢  不  等等
I was really worried... No, hold on,

1215
01:05:57,950 --> 01:05:59,080
我真沒擔心
I really wasn't.

1216
01:06:00,240 --> 01:06:01,830
我以前救過你
I was there for you before.

1217
01:06:02,600 --> 01:06:04,160
下一次我還會救你
I'll be there for you again.

1218
01:06:06,550 --> 01:06:08,370
不論多少次我都會救你
I'll always be there for you.

1219
01:06:10,640 --> 01:06:11,920
這是我的錯
This was my fault.

1220
01:06:12,920 --> 01:06:14,550
這與你無關
It was nothing to do with you.

1221
01:06:15,370 --> 01:06:16,600
入獄一周
A week in a prison cell,

1222
01:06:16,600 --> 01:06:18,580
- 我該意識到的  - 意識到什麼
- I should have realised. - Realised what?

1223
01:06:18,850 --> 01:06:19,740
對你來說
That, in your case,

1224
01:06:19,750 --> 01:06:23,160
單獨監禁其實是和死敵關在一起
solitary confinement is locking you up with your worst enemy.

1225
01:06:23,160 --> 01:06:24,620
我的神啊
Oh, for God's sake!

1226
01:06:24,880 --> 01:06:26,160
嗎啡還是可卡因
Morphine or cocaine?

1227
01:06:28,880 --> 01:06:29,990
你說什麼
What did you say?

1228
01:06:30,490 --> 01:06:31,670
我什麼也沒說
I didn't say anything.

1229
01:06:31,950 --> 01:06:33,150
不  你說了  你說
No, you did, you said...

1230
01:06:33,950 --> 01:06:36,550
今天是什麼  嗎啡還是可卡因
Which is it today? Morphine or cocaine.

1231
01:06:39,720 --> 01:06:40,550
福爾摩斯
'Holmes?'

1232
01:06:40,720 --> 01:06:43,140
嗎啡還是可卡因  今天是什麼
Morphine or cocaine - which is it today?

1233
01:06:43,990 --> 01:06:45,510
回答我  該死的
Answer me, damn it!

1234
01:06:47,200 --> 01:06:48,680
莫里亞蒂來過
Moriarty was here.

1235
01:06:49,710 --> 01:06:50,810
莫里亞蒂死了
Moriarty's dead.

1236
01:06:53,750 --> 01:06:55,140
我剛剛在飛機上
I was on a jet.

1237
01:06:55,940 --> 01:06:56,840
什麼上
A what?

1238
01:06:56,960 --> 01:06:58,770
你也在  還有麥考夫
You were there, and Mycroft.

1239
01:06:59,770 --> 01:07:01,740
你就沒出過門  福爾摩斯
You haven't left these rooms, Holmes.

1240
01:07:02,930 --> 01:07:05,800
連動都沒動一下
You...haven't...moved.

1241
01:07:05,970 --> 01:07:08,730
告訴我  是嗎啡還是可卡因
Now, tell me, morphine or cocaine?

1242
01:07:10,300 --> 01:07:13,560
可卡因  7%的
Cocaine. A 7% solution.

1243
01:07:14,550 --> 01:07:16,040
- 想來點嗎  - 不想
- Would you care to try it? - No.

1244
01:07:16,320 --> 01:07:18,510
但我十分想把這兒所有的
But I would quite like to find every ounce of the stuff

1245
01:07:18,510 --> 01:07:20,380
這破玩意兒都找到然後倒窗外
in your possession and pour it out of the window.

1246
01:07:21,050 --> 01:07:22,520
那我會想阻止你
I should be inclined to stop you.

1247
01:07:22,520 --> 01:07:25,530
那我將用強有力的方式提醒你
Then you would be reminded, quite forcibly,

1248
01:07:25,730 --> 01:07:28,830
我們兩個中誰是軍人  誰是癮君子
which of us is a soldier and which of us a drug addict.

1249
01:07:29,100 --> 01:07:31,260
你不是軍人  你是個醫生
You're not a soldier, you are a doctor.

1250
01:07:31,260 --> 01:07:32,390
我是個軍醫  所以說我可以
I'm an army doctor, which means I could

1251
01:07:32,390 --> 01:07:35,130
一邊掰斷你每一根骨頭  一邊叫出它的學名
break every bone in your body while naming them.

1252
01:07:35,450 --> 01:07:39,770
親愛的華生  你的感情干擾了你的判斷
My dear Watson, you are allowing emotion to cloud your judgment.

1253
01:07:39,780 --> 01:07:40,900
辦案不吸毒
Never on a case.

1254
01:07:41,800 --> 01:07:43,530
你保證過的  辦案不吸毒
You promised me, never on a case.

1255
01:07:43,530 --> 01:07:45,230
不  那是出自
No, I just said that

1256
01:07:45,230 --> 01:07:46,790
- 你的一篇故事  - 聽著
- in one of your stories. - Listen,

1257
01:07:47,700 --> 01:07:49,870
我很樂意為你扮演捧哏
I'm happy to play the fool for you.

1258
01:07:49,950 --> 01:07:52,830
我可以像笨蛋一樣跟著你到處跑
I will run along behind you like some halfwit,

1259
01:07:52,830 --> 01:07:54,710
襯托你的聰明  如果你需要的話
making you look clever, if that's what you need.

1260
01:07:54,710 --> 01:07:56,560
但看在上帝分上
But dear God above,

1261
01:07:56,710 --> 01:07:59,940
你得給自己定個更高的標準
you will hold yourself to a higher standard!

1262
01:07:59,940 --> 01:08:02,170
- 為什麼  - 因為人們需要你那麼做
- Why? - Because people need you to.

1263
01:08:02,170 --> 01:08:04,350
什麼人  為什麼  就因為你的蠢故事
What people, why? Because of your idiot stories?

1264
01:08:04,350 --> 01:08:06,910
沒錯  就因為我的蠢故事
Yes, because of my "idiot stories".

1265
01:08:07,090 --> 01:08:08,280
福爾摩斯先生
Mr Holmes!

1266
01:08:09,490 --> 01:08:11,930
福爾摩斯先生  電報  福爾摩斯先生
Mr Holmes, telegram, Mr Holmes.

1267
01:08:20,570 --> 01:08:21,820
怎麼了  出什麼事了
What is it? What's wrong?

1268
01:08:22,820 --> 01:08:25,350
- 是瑪麗  - 瑪麗  她怎麼了
- It's Mary. - Mary? What about her?

1269
01:08:25,350 --> 01:08:27,590
- 她很有可能陷入了危險  - 危險
- It's entirely possible she's in danger. - Danger?

1270
01:08:27,590 --> 01:08:28,960
一刻也不能耽擱了
There's not a moment to lose.

1271
01:08:29,620 --> 01:08:31,630
這是你吸毒的幻覺嗎
Is this the cocaine talking?

1272
01:08:32,150 --> 01:08:33,270
瑪麗能有什麼危險
What danger could Mary be in?

1273
01:08:33,270 --> 01:08:36,380
- 她肯定只是去拜訪朋友了  - 快走
- I'm sure she's just visiting with friends. - Come on!

1274
01:08:42,180 --> 01:08:43,650
到底怎麼了
What is happening?

1275
01:08:43,730 --> 01:08:45,580
你這狀況真的可以嗎
Are you even in a fit state?

1276
01:08:46,070 --> 01:08:48,700
為瑪麗當然可以  這毋庸置疑  華生
For Mary, of course. Never doubt that, Watson.

1277
01:08:49,760 --> 01:08:50,810
毋庸置疑
Never that.

1278
01:08:52,010 --> 01:08:52,920
福爾摩斯
Holmes?

1279
01:08:53,160 --> 01:08:54,330
我沒事  我沒事
I'm fine. I'm fine!

1280
01:08:56,230 --> 01:08:57,580
別戴那頂
Not that one!

1281
01:08:58,930 --> 01:08:59,760
戴這頂
This one.

1282
01:09:00,780 --> 01:09:02,220
- 為什麼  - 你是夏洛克·福爾摩斯
- Why? - You're Sherlock Holmes.

1283
01:09:02,220 --> 01:09:03,620
戴你該戴的帽子吧
Wear the damn hat.

1284
01:09:10,970 --> 01:09:13,210
馬車  馬車
Cab! Cab!

1285
01:09:16,390 --> 01:09:18,070
說吧  她在哪
So tell me, where is she?

1286
01:09:18,780 --> 01:09:20,970
告訴我  到底是怎麼回事
You must tell me, what's going on?!

1287
01:09:20,970 --> 01:09:22,070
我的好華生啊
Oh, good old Watson!

1288
01:09:22,070 --> 01:09:24,560
你不問問題我們這些閒暇時間該怎麼過啊
How would we fill the time if you didn't ask questions?!

1289
01:09:24,560 --> 01:09:27,250
夏洛克  快告訴我  我妻子在哪
Sherlock, tell me where my bloody wife is,

1290
01:09:27,250 --> 01:09:29,900
你個自大的混蛋  否則我真跟你動手
you pompous prick, or I'll punch your lights out!

1291
01:09:31,670 --> 01:09:33,010
福爾摩斯  她在哪
Holmes, where is she?

1292
01:09:34,930 --> 01:09:36,510
一間廢棄教堂
A de-sanctified church.

1293
01:09:36,510 --> 01:09:38,030
她覺得她找到了答案
She thinks she's found the solution and,

1294
01:09:38,030 --> 01:09:39,210
也正因此
for no better reason than that,

1295
01:09:39,210 --> 01:09:41,710
她讓自己陷入了巨大的危險
she's put herself in the path of considerable danger.

1296
01:09:42,130 --> 01:09:43,910
老婆選得真好
What an excellent choice of wife.

1297
01:09:56,950 --> 01:09:58,160
搞什麼
What the devil?!

1298
01:09:58,240 --> 01:09:59,370
我找到他們了
I've found them.

1299
01:10:08,320 --> 01:10:09,290
這是什麼啊  瑪麗
What is all this, Mary?

1300
01:10:09,290 --> 01:10:11,500
是一切的核心  約翰
This is the heart of it all, John.

1301
01:10:11,560 --> 01:10:13,210
陰謀的核心
The heart of the conspiracy.

1302
01:10:33,710 --> 01:10:36,440
老天爺啊  這是什麼地方
Great God, what is this place?

1303
01:10:37,130 --> 01:10:38,850
而且你為什麼會在這兒
And what the devil are you doing here?!

1304
01:10:38,850 --> 01:10:40,760
我一直在調查
I've been making enquiries.

1305
01:10:41,300 --> 01:10:43,090
應福爾摩斯先生之請
Mr Holmes asked me.

1306
01:10:43,200 --> 01:10:44,300
福爾摩斯  你怎麼能這麼做
Holmes, how could you?

1307
01:10:44,300 --> 01:10:46,420
不  不是他  聰明的那個
No, not him, the clever one.

1308
01:10:47,050 --> 01:10:48,060
我認為很明顯
It seemed obvious to me

1309
01:10:48,060 --> 01:10:50,570
這件事一個人無法完成
that this business could not be managed alone.

1310
01:10:50,570 --> 01:10:53,460
我認為瑞克萊蒂太太有幫手
My theory is that Mrs Ricoletti had help.

1311
01:10:53,460 --> 01:10:54,920
她的朋友
Help from her friends.

1312
01:10:55,060 --> 01:10:57,770
- 漂亮  瑪麗  "聰明的那個"  - 我
- Bravo, Mary. "The clever one?" - I...

1313
01:10:58,310 --> 01:11:00,230
我以為我要失去你了
I thought I was losing you.

1314
01:11:01,400 --> 01:11:03,250
我以為我們
I thought perhaps we were...

1315
01:11:03,850 --> 01:11:06,010
- 在冷戰  - 是你先搬出去的
- neglecting each other. - Well, you're the one who moved out.

1316
01:11:06,020 --> 01:11:08,170
我是在跟瑪麗說話
I was talking to Mary.

1317
01:11:09,260 --> 01:11:10,780
你怎麼為麥考夫辦事了
You're working for Mycroft?

1318
01:11:10,960 --> 01:11:13,060
他想監督他的瘋弟弟
He likes to keep an eye on his mad sibling.

1319
01:11:13,060 --> 01:11:15,590
而且手頭正好有個間諜  你從來沒發現
And he had a spy to hand. Has it never occurred to you

1320
01:11:15,590 --> 01:11:17,690
你妻子的能力遠超普通護士嗎
your wife is excessively skilled for a nurse?

1321
01:11:17,690 --> 01:11:18,720
他當然沒發現
Of course it hasn't,

1322
01:11:18,910 --> 01:11:21,340
因為他瞭解護士的本事
because he knows what a nurse is capable of.

1323
01:11:21,370 --> 01:11:22,280
你又是什麼時候發現的
When did it occur to you?

1324
01:11:22,280 --> 01:11:23,890
剛發現  不好意思
Only now, I'm afraid.

1325
01:11:23,940 --> 01:11:25,400
肯定很痛苦吧
Must be difficult,

1326
01:11:25,650 --> 01:11:27,350
當天才的笨弟弟
being the slow little brother.

1327
01:11:27,350 --> 01:11:29,840
也該跟上節奏了  聊夠了  辦正事
Time I sped up. Enough chatter, let's concentrate.

1328
01:11:30,020 --> 01:11:32,770
好吧  這是在幹什麼
Yes, all right. What's all this about?

1329
01:11:33,400 --> 01:11:34,710
他們想做什麼
What do they want to accomplish?

1330
01:11:34,710 --> 01:11:36,320
進去弄個明白吧
Why don't we go and find out.

1331
01:11:55,690 --> 01:11:57,730
抱歉  見到鑼不敲就難受
Sorry! I can never resist a gong.

1332
01:11:57,730 --> 01:12:00,180
- 更無法抗拒戲劇性場面  - 誰能想到呢
- Or a touch of the dramatic. - Never have guessed!

1333
01:12:00,760 --> 01:12:03,970
但你們好像跟我一樣  喜歡戲劇性
Though it seems you share my enthusiasm in that regard.

1334
01:12:05,650 --> 01:12:06,780
真棒
Excellent.

1335
01:12:07,330 --> 01:12:09,080
一流的劇場
Superlative theatre.

1336
01:12:09,840 --> 01:12:12,220
場面令人讚歎
I applaud the spectacle.

1337
01:12:15,400 --> 01:12:16,940
艾米麗婭·瑞克萊蒂飲彈自盡
Emelia Ricoletti shot herself,

1338
01:12:16,940 --> 01:12:20,600
然後起死回生  殺死了她丈夫
then apparently returned from the grave and killed her husband.

1339
01:12:21,010 --> 01:12:21,970
那麼...
So...

1340
01:12:22,890 --> 01:12:24,070
是怎麼回事呢
how was it done?

1341
01:12:25,100 --> 01:12:27,050
整理一下這一事件吧
Let's take the events in order.

1342
01:12:30,100 --> 01:12:32,140
瑞克萊蒂太太用最快的速度
Mrs. Ricoletti gets everyone's attention

1343
01:12:32,140 --> 01:12:34,250
- 吸引了所有人的注意  - 你
- in very efficient fashion. - You!

1344
01:12:37,270 --> 01:12:38,300
你
You?!

1345
01:12:38,910 --> 01:12:39,990
還是我
Or me?

1346
01:12:40,990 --> 01:12:42,980
她把一把槍塞進嘴裡
She places one of the revolvers in her mouth,

1347
01:12:42,980 --> 01:12:45,100
開火的卻是槍口朝下的另一把槍
while actually firing the other into the ground.

1348
01:12:45,100 --> 01:12:47,210
她的同謀向窗簾上噴血
An accomplice sprays the curtains with blood

1349
01:12:47,210 --> 01:12:48,550
這樣樓下驚慌失措的民眾
and thus her apparent suicide

1350
01:12:48,550 --> 01:12:50,970
就都目睹了她自殺的景象
is witnessed by the frightened crowd below.

1351
01:12:52,880 --> 01:12:53,760
另找一具
A substitute corpse,

1352
01:12:53,760 --> 01:12:55,770
跟瑞克萊蒂太太非常相似的屍體
bearing a strong resemblance to Mrs. Ricoletti

1353
01:12:55,770 --> 01:12:58,300
來代替她  稍後被送進停屍房
takes her place and is later transported to the morgue,

1354
01:12:58,300 --> 01:13:01,820
這種自殺的小案子蘇格蘭場也沒什麼興趣
a grubby little suicide of little interest to Scotland Yard.

1355
01:13:01,820 --> 01:13:06,030
同時真的瑞克萊蒂太太悄悄溜走
Meanwhile, the real Mrs. Ricoletti slips away.

1356
01:13:10,520 --> 01:13:12,530
真正聰明的是這步
Now comes the really clever part.

1357
01:13:12,530 --> 01:13:15,580
瑞克萊蒂太太說服一位元認識她的馬車夫
Mrs. Ricoletti persuaded a cab driver, someone who knew her,

1358
01:13:15,580 --> 01:13:18,730
拉她去丈夫最喜歡的鴉片館外等他
to intercept her husband outside his favourite opium den.

1359
01:13:19,140 --> 01:13:22,180
完美的舞臺  完美的一齣戲
The perfect stage for a perfect drama.

1360
01:13:22,660 --> 01:13:24,250
你是誰  你要幹什麼
Who are you? What do you want?

1361
01:13:26,810 --> 01:13:27,690
艾米麗婭
Emelia?

1362
01:13:28,790 --> 01:13:29,320
救命
Help!

1363
01:13:29,320 --> 01:13:31,520
身份得到完全確認
A perfect positive identification.

1364
01:13:31,730 --> 01:13:34,010
已故的瑞克萊蒂太太起死回生
The late Mrs. Ricoletti has returned from the grave

1365
01:13:34,010 --> 01:13:36,170
加上精湛的化妝
